{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述小鱼儿与铁心兰在夜行途中遭遇江湖奇人黑蜘蛛，黑蜘蛛以\"神蛛凌空，银丝渡虚\"的独门轻功来去飘忽，警告小鱼儿将有大祸临头后飘然而去。铁心兰认出马屁股上碧磷蛇印记，解释这是\"十二星相\"中食鹿神君的杀人标志。两人逃至山村借宿，小鱼儿凭观察识破假老婆婆端烫碗不觉烫的破绽，发现饭中藏蛇、老农夫妇已被害。途中又遭碧蛇神君设伏，小鱼儿被蛇身藏剑割伤中毒。碧蛇神君现身逼索藏宝图，小鱼儿机智地将羊皮纸吞入腹中，以死相胁与碧蛇神君周旋。危急时刻，神秘的小仙女声音传来，碧蛇神君闻声色变，小鱼儿绝处逢生。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "大哥？……你个子比我还小，该叫我大哥才是。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "江湖中人求我要叫我一声大哥的人也不知有多少，但却被我一个个踢回去了，我要你叫我，你还不愿意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "很好！……黑老弟，你的本事不小……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你叫我什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "黑老弟，咱们喝两杯去如何？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知你现在已将有大祸临头，除了我外，没有人能帮你，你若叫我一声大哥，不知有多少好处。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "黑老弟，我有什么大祸临头，你且说来听听。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，我本来想帮你个忙的，但你既然要在我面前充老大，我也就犯不着再管你的事了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪他口气这么大，轻功果然有两下子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "岂止有两下子，他这手独门轻功，'神蛛凌空，银丝渡虚'，在江湖中简直没有第二个人能比得上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这种功夫有什么巧妙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他袖中所藏的，据说真是南海千年神蛛所结的丝，又坚又韧，刀剑难伤，他将这蛛丝藏在一个特制的机簧筒中，手一扬，蛛丝就飞了出去，最远据说可达一二十丈，而蛛丝顶端的银针，无论钉住什么东西，他人立刻就能跟着到那里，当真可说是来去飘忽，快如鬼魅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这小子非但人古怪得有趣，所练的功夫也古怪得有趣，却不知他年纪竟是大是小？为什么如此喜欢充老。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "江湖中没有一个人瞧见过他的脸，更没有人知道他年纪，只知他最恨别人说他小，谁要犯了他这毛病，马上就要倒霉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我怎么还没有倒霉？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这倒是怪事，他倒真像是和你有缘，否则，就凭你叫他那几声老弟，他只怕已经要割下你的舌头了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但这人从来不说假话，他说咱们立刻就将有大祸临头，只怕……只怕也不会说假。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "哪有什么大祸临头，你别听他鬼话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你瞧见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "没有什么……哈哈，哪有什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我知道你一打哈哈，说的就不是真话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不想我这毛病竟被你瞧出了……我这毛病是从小被一个人传染的，竟一直到现在还改不过来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那么，你究竟瞧见了什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "也没什么了不起的东西，你不瞧也罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我知道你不让我瞧，是怕我着急，但我若不瞧，就会更着急……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "唉……女人，你要瞧，就瞧瞧吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "蛇……碧磷蛇……青海之灵，食鹿神君！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不懂的……不懂的……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "一条小蛇就算是真的，也没什么可怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "真的不可怕，这假的才可怕。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不怕真的怕假的，为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这碧磷蛇就是那'青海之灵，食鹿神君'的标志，标志所在，他人就不远了，他人既不远，祸事就真的要来了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这食鹿神君又是什么玩意呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可听过'十二星相'这名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "好像听过，又好像没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这'十二星相'乃是近三十年，江湖中最残酷、最狠毒的一批强盗，他们平日极少下手，但若瞧见值得下手的东西，被他们瞧中的人便再也休想跑得了。三十年来，据说'十二星相'只有一次失手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这条蛇自然就是'十二星相'中的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，这'食鹿神君'，正是'十二星相'中最阴毒、最狡猾的一人，他的老窝就在青海……唉！我本该早已想到他要向我下手的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "为什么你早就该想到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "十二星相惟一失手的一次，据说就是栽在燕南天手上，他们若知道燕南天有藏剑谱留下，又怎肯放过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不想你年纪虽小，知道的事却不少。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我很小的时候，就出来闯荡江湖，知道的江湖秘事，自然比别人多些，你将来在江湖走动，便会知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "知道的越多，就害怕的越多，倒不如索性什么都不知道，无论遇着什么人，都可以不管三七二十一先和他拼了再说。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但我们现在既然知道了，又该怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "咱们此刻既拼不过他，自然惟有走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "走？……能走得了么？……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "小白菜，辛苦你了，抱歉抱歉！……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "老汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "看来今天又是个好天气，该把棉被拿出来晒晒了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lao_han",
      "text": "老丈可有什么吃喝的，赏给我兄妹一些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "老汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小官人说话真客气，只要不嫌老汉家里茶饭粗陋，就快请进来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不想这里的乡下人倒好客得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "瞧见你这么可爱的孩子，话又说得这么甜，无论你要什么，只怕没人能狠得下心拒绝你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "只怕别人是瞧在你这病美人的面子，他虽是个老头子，但却没有瞎眼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_han",
      "speaker_name": "老汉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "两位稍坐，老汉瞧瞧老婆子饭可煮好了没。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "两位小客人先用吧，莫客气，饭凉了就不好吃了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "既是如此，我兄妹就不客气。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "真烫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这是干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "蛇……十二星相！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好狠……好毒……唉，好险。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人看来竟比我还坏十倍，竟连这老人家都不肯放过。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我……我早就知道咱们跑不了的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "小白菜，莫要怕，这些恶人害不死你的，也休想害得死我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好险！……好险，咱们只要吃进一粒饭，就活不到现在了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "但咱们现在还是好好的活着！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你是怎么会发觉的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你端起饭碗，还烫得不能留手，那老婆子却安安稳稳从厨房里一路捧出来，这双手没有练过毒砂掌一类的功夫才怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "真是什么事都逃不过你这双眼睛。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "莫慌，捉蛇打狗的本事我最在行！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "幸好你不是女人，女人可都是怕蛇的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你那柄匕首拿来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小心些，莫要被蛇血溅在身上。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "哼！……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你这是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我终于还是上当了！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "原……原来这条蛇早已死了，那恶魔竟在蛇身里藏着一柄软剑，剑上有剧毒，你一捏蛇身，里面的剑锋就割伤了你。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你真聪明，真是天才儿童。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "幸……幸好你……你发觉得早，已将毒血放出，只怕已没……没事了吧？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "没事了……半个时辰后，什么都没了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你胡说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这毒是没有救的，我若不放血，此刻已要去见那老头子了，纵然放了血，也拖不着半个时辰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这毒有救的，你根本不知道……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我从小就在使毒的大名家群中打滚，我若不知道，天下还有准知道！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "既然如此，你就该能配解药。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我自然能配解药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你原来又在吓我！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "但这解药却要三个月才配得好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你现在还有心情开玩笑，你……你……你叫我怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你简直不是人！你竟对自己的生死都要开玩笑，却不管别人心里如何，我恨死你……恨死你了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "小臭蛇，你瞧见了么！这就是那藏宝图，你想不想要？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这迟早是我的，我并不着急。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "这真已迟早是你的了么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若趁早双手奉上，本座只怕还会救你的命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "是，是，我很相信……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就给他吧，反正……反正咱们已用不着了！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "还是这女子聪明。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "是，是，她聪明，我却很笨！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "吐出来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "吐不出来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这是找死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "这藏宝图世上只有一张，也只有我一人将它看熟了，你若让我死，一辈子都休想瞧那藏宝图一眼。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "我若是你，此刻就该将解药拿出来了，只要我活着，说不定还会将那藏宝图画出来，死人的手是不会动的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你只当本座真的要被你这小鬼要挟住了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "假的么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那羊皮纸又薄又韧，你纵然吞下去，也还是好好的在你肚子里，本座只要剖开你的肚子，还怕拿不到？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "你不能这么做……你不能！……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "谁说不能？你瞧着吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "捉蛇打狗你最在行，开膛剖腹却是我最在行的，但你只管放心，我这一剑刺下，绝不会要你的命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "多谢多谢！……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我就算将你肚子剖开，将那羊皮纸拿了出来，你还未必死的……我要叫你慢慢地死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "但你动手时却要小心些，我今天早上吃了条蛇祖宗在肚子里，还未消化，你切莫不小心伤了你的祖宗。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鬼，临死还要贫嘴！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你妄动气力，毒性发作更快，死得更早。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鬼！你还有什么花样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剖肚子乃人生一大快事也，不想我江小鱼竟在无意中得之！……",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
